  - deterministic Fight Caves simulation, contracts, combat, pathing, waves
- `demo-env/`
  - Raylib viewer, HUD, assets, replay tooling
- `training-env/`
  - PufferLib adapter, reward assembly, backend build glue
- `pufferlib_4/`
  - local runtime dependency tree, checkpoints, logs, W&B artifacts

Dependencies:
- Python 3.12
- local venv at `runescape-rl/.venv`
- PyTorch / NumPy / W&B / local PufferLib
- CMake + C compiler
- CUDA/cuDNN for GPU training
- Raylib vendored in `runescape-rl/demo-env/raylib`

